{
  "stem": "2353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, I would love it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they found an old gym suit for me, and I had to jump barefoot, nobody could fit my big feet, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that was the first time I had done this in so long, and I-- it was just-- it was heavenly, [LAUGHS] you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't think I ever jumped that-- that well because I was just so relieved that I was into this again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So right away, I was invited to join the track club, and that sealed my fate there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father left, and I had found a place where I could get room and board, and I went to school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what was nice, that I was accepted in the school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had quite a few friends there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, not once, not once was I invited to somebody's home, and I still wonder why not?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, why was I discriminated against in England?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just-- I tried to get away from that in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Why was I discriminated against?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't figure out why it was never invited to anybody's house even though we were very friendly in school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had lunch together and, you know, went shopping together, all this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That bothered me, did not endear me to the English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So what year is this now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was in the fall of 1933.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I competed for the school and won everything in sight, and then, somehow-- I don't know how that worked out anymore-- they-- they enrolled me or entered me in the-- the British Championships, which was on June 30, 1934, and I won.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had come to watch me, I thought.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
